description.narrative: Communication initiatives and advocacy efforts resulted in increased awareness about child rights and recommitment of the Inter-Parliamentary Union (IPU) and the Serbian Government to upholding and protecting the rights and guiding principles enshrined in the CRC. Communication support to programme and donor initiatives included the production and dissemination of multimedia products. The integration of digital platforms resulted in exceeded targets, with 54% increase in the success rate compared to 2018. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:13/12/2019
